title: Celebrities’ most expensive Valentine’s Day gifts ever [Video]
text: India Newzstreet Media 13 February 2017 When it comes to showering love, celebrities with bulky bank accounts don’t care how far their cash will go as long as their loved ones feel special. Here we bring you the list of celebs who presented their partners some of the most luxurious and outrageously priced gifts on the Valentine’s Day. Reblog
